    "actionRequired": null
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "toggles": {},
    "dialogue": { "speed": "slow", "show": true, "characterName": "shm", "text": "and maybe if i understood how i was being perceived, i could control that." },
    "actionRequired": null
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "toggles": {},
    "dialogue": { "speed": "slow", "show": true, "characterName": "shm", "text": "or i could.... i could explain." },
    "actionRequired": null
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "toggles": { "race": true, "gender": true, "age": true },
    "dialogue": { "show": true, "characterName": "shm", "text": "years before i had the words to articulate why, it bothered me that when people looked at me, they were perceiving things that i didn't realize were... there" },
    "actionRequired": null
  },
  {
    "id": 23,
    "toggles": {},
    "dialogue": { "show": true, "characterName": "shm", "text": "and i uh, i grew up in a very white community. and i love that community." },
    "actionRequired": null
  },
  {
    "id": 24,
    "toggles": {},
